message.distributionDefaultInviterIdTip.message: User ID of the default inviter. If no inviter_id parameter is carried in the distribution link, this user ID is used by default as the inviter.

message.distributionForceInviterIdTip.message: User ID of the forced inviter. If this ID is set, regardless of whether the distribution link carries the inviter_id parameter, this user ID is forcibly used as the inviter.

message.originTip.message: Site domain, bound to site configuration and domain. The site domain cannot be changed.

message.titleTip.message: Site title, displayed in the browser tab.

message.descriptionTip.message: Site description, located in site metadata, used for site SEO optimization.

message.logoTip.message: Site logo, displayed at the top of the site menu when expanded.

message.faviconTip.message: Site favicon, displayed in the browser tab.

message.adminsTip.message: Site administrators ID, by default the user who first creates the site becomes an administrator. Only site administrators can manage the site.

message.adminsTip2.message: You can add or delete administrator IDs here. Visit https://auth.acedata.cloud to view user IDs.

message.keywordsTip.message: Site keywords, located in site metadata, used for site SEO optimization.

message.keywordsTip2.message: You can add or delete website keywords here. The more accurate the keywords, the better for SEO optimization.

message.featuresI18n.message: Toggle multi-language support on or off. When disabled, users can only use the default language.
